author: Caitlin Huston
title: Pure Storage down 2.5%, trading below IPO issue price range
text: Shares of Pure Storage PSTG, -1.94% were down 2.5% Thursday morning, causing the stock to trade below its initial public offering issue price range of $16 to $18. The stock was trading at $15.61, a day after it went public, and below its IPO issue price of $17. In its market debut yesterday, the stock opened at $16.74 and closed at $16.01.
